headline: FlexShares® Announces Liquidation of an Exchange Traded Fund
summary: CHICAGO, January 03, 2025--Northern Trust’s FlexShares Exchange Traded Funds announced the liquidation and termination of the FlexShares International Quality Dividend Defensive Index Fund (Ticker: IQDE) (the "Fund"). Prior to and through the close of regular trading (the "Close of Trading") on the NYSE Arca, Inc. ("NYSE Arca") on or about January 21, 2025 (the "Closing Date"), the Fund will undertake the process of closing down and liquidating its portfolio.

headline: Major Regional Bank Industry Healthy: 4 Stocks to Gain in 2025
summary: High funding costs and poor asset quality will hurt the Zacks Major Regional Banks. Yet, interest rate cuts, decent loan demand, solid economic growth and business restructuring will likely aid industry players like USB, TFC, BK and NTRS.
